Package: biorrxiv
Type: Package
Title: R client for the bioRxiv API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nicholas", "Fraser", email = "nicholasmfraser@gmail.com")
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: biorrxiv is an R client for interacting with the bioRxiv API
    (https://api.biorxiv.org/). Functions include retrieving metadata of
    preprints, details of published papers associated with preprints, and
    summary and usage statistics. Note that the bioRxiv API is currently
    in beta development, and thus subject to change.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/nicholasmfraser/biorrxiv
BugReports: https://github.com/nicholasmfraser/biorrxiv/issues
Imports:
    httr (>= 1.4)
    jsonlite (>= 1.5),
